{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"614","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"大學善盡社會責任 地方創生好樣的","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>04:10 2020/01/11 </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>中國時報 林志成</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B81.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 533px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>海洋大學協助基隆八斗子恢復「元宵祭」。（海洋大學提供／林志成台北傳真）</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B82.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 451px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>科大學生到校外有機農場進行實作課程。（高科大提供／林志成台北傳真）</span></span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>大學也要盡社會責任！高科大過去<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>年來，<span lang='EN-US'>30</span>多個老師、<span lang='EN-US'>1000</span>多個學生幫燕巢地區果農解決缺工及行銷問題，未來要協助他們自立及永續發展；海洋大學則幫忙基隆八斗子及馬祖漁港活化，未來會擴及到宜蘭壯圍及新北市貢寮的漁港。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>高科大產學長蔡匡忠表示，他們第一校區就位於燕巢，當地有很多種植芭樂、蜜棗的果農，但他們主要是老年人，面臨缺工、行銷不夠好等問題，學校行銷系、環境安全系及通識課程的老師和學生們，利用自身的專業幫助果農。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>例如，蜜棗在農曆年前後是生產期，學校就開發招工<span lang='EN-US'>APP</span>，果農如果需要工人，可透過<span lang='EN-US'>APP</span>找，也提供學生打工機會；開發以燕巢在地品牌聚焦的加工品「醜芭怪」芭樂冰棒，第一批<span lang='EN-US'>1.6</span>萬支在去年<span lang='EN-US'>7</span>月至<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>月賣完，第二批預計今年<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月上市。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>另近年來蜜蜂數量減少，果樹難授粉，影響產量。高科大師生幫忙培養取代蜜蜂的昆蟲，並將廢棄的果樹樹枝做成文創商品，除了解決授粉困境，也創造新利潤。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>海洋大學則從<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>年多前開始推動「三漁（漁業、漁村及漁民）興旺－國際藍色經濟示範區」計畫，協助活化八斗子漁港及馬祖漁港。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>海洋大學教務長張文哲表示，八斗子漁港有<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>多間珊瑚化石做的房子，曾因為沒有使用而廢棄，學校師生和居民共同去整理，現在這些房子已成觀光景點。另八斗子中斷<span lang='EN-US'>40</span>多年的傳統祭典「元宵祭」，也在海大師生努力下，恢復舉辦。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>張文哲又說，馬祖最有名的藍眼淚，被海洋大學老師解密是夜行蟲為安心吃東西而放出的保護色；同時，海大馬祖校區的<span lang='EN-US'>80</span>多位學生，成為地方政府辦活動的好幫手，為當地帶來活力。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>:https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20200111000741-260114?chdtv</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-01-13","clk_count":"31"}},"__N_SSG":true}